{"tid":2317064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始籲僱主體諒員工因強制檢測而未能上班 禁足令前離開居民都「無辦法」","createTime":"2020-12-08T09:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T16:32:37.000Z","uid":291865,"like":8,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"02f101c06e4ef6a195d39d9a25d9c8dd5a38f7f8","tid":2317064,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1564228_1_20201208171943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1564228_1_20201208171943.jpg&h=e5e79096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，若政府發出限制與檢測宣告，令員工無法上班，希望僱主能夠體諒，因有關員工並非故意，而是衞生署經風險評估而作出的決定，涉及到公共衞生的因素。<br />\n<br />\n被問到如果在政府作出宣告前，有關處所內的居民已經離開，這些居民是否都受到宣告約束。陳肇始表示，如果在衞生署作出評估前，有居民已經離開都「無辦法」，但她呼籲有關人士不要再走動，因為如果他們真是受感染，會令病毒擴散，對疫情控制並無幫助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564228-20201208.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564228-20201208.htm&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=994f0d21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564228-20201208.htm&h=25f37e8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564228-20201208.htm</a>"},{"pid":"69fb1b11cd79602e77d8027e81c34b147410f468","tid":2317064,"uid":143241,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:56:21.000Z","msg":"屌你哋班廢人都嘥鳩氣,弱撚智！"},{"pid":"778d50a34af0178e8304241e8136e11ed887f1fa","tid":2317064,"uid":57488,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:57:31.000Z","msg":"籲籲籲你老母咩<br />\n夠薑嘅咪立法拉晒啲叫人返工嘅老細囉"},{"pid":"90180c2a25f70600261f0db0470055004a005206","tid":2317064,"uid":52006,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"老細：假照扣"},{"pid":"60bcf7c9ebcc6b913c4a334926473b1473aec289","tid":2317064,"uid